    "title": "Setting up the hardware",
    "content": "The following table shows the target hardware for the application projects. | Project Name | Board | . | pic32cx_mtsh_db.X | PIC32CXMTSH Development Board | . |   |   | . Setting up PIC32CXMTSH Development Board . | TC0_CH0 generates the PWM waveform on pin PA02 | TC0_CH1 is configured in capture mode with the input signal connected to pin PA31 | Use a jumper wire to connect “Pin 10 of Xplained Pro Header (TC0_TIOA0)” to “Pin 1 of mikroBUS Socket (TC0_TIOA1)” | Connect the Debug USB port on the board to the computer using a micro USB cable | . ",
    "url": "http://localhost:4000/csp_apps_pic32cx_mt/apps/tc/tc_capture_mode/readme.html#setting-up-the-hardware",
